    "No MeowGram here — JPEG/HEIC re-compression usually destroys them. Ask the sender for the original PNG.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kein MeowGram — JPEG/HEIC-Neukomprimierung zerstört sie meist. Bitte den Absender um das Original-PNG."
